'''M3-D2''' was a [[Droid/Legends|droid]] inserted into [[Jabba's Palace/Legends|Jabba's Palace]] by the [[Whiphid/Legends|Whiphid]] known as [[Lady/Legends|Lady]] [[Valarian/Legends|Valarian]] in an effort to pursuade [[Sy Snootles/Legends|Sy Snootles]] to act as a [[Spy/Legends|spy]] against [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]]. M3-D2 also acted as a contact for many of Lady Valarian's other spies.

